longBusinessSummary: Freemelt Holding AB (publ) engages in the metal 3D-printing business in Europe and North America. The company provides asset condition monitoring, connected machine insight, remote support, asset maintenance, and asset management services. It also offers Pixelmelt, a software for metal 3D printing; open source platform; eÂ–MELT, a printer for industrial production; and Freemelt ONE, a printer for research institutes and universities. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
